com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit

Class CampaignKitNotifier.CKEventType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum
      • com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.CampaignKitNotifier.CKEventType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable
    Enclosing interface:
    CampaignKitNotifier

    public static final class CampaignKitNotifier.CKEventType
extends Enum
    A category reflecting what type of event occured to trigger didDetectPlace. Currently, beacons will only trigger the CKEventDidRangeBeacons event. And geofences will only trigger the CKEventDidEnterRegion, CKEventDidExitRegion, CKEventDidDetectStateInside, and CKEventDidDetectStateOutside events.
    See Also:
    CampaignKitNotifier.didDetectPlace(com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.Place, com.radiusnetworks.campaignkit.CampaignKitNotifier.CKEventType), Serialized Form
